txt.en: A bounty notice is pinned to the board, stamped with the royal seal of Gondor:\n\n'An extremely dangerous species of leech has been discovered in the swamps of Dath Nethryn. The Conquest of Gorgoroth requests an adventurer to travel to Lhingris and exterminate them. They are known to lurk beneath the water's surface and will attack if the water is disturbed.'
Voracious leeches can be found in the waters of Dath Nethryn.\n\nYou should defeat voracious leeches.
The Conquest of Gorgoroth has encountered a particularly dangerous species of leeches and requests an adventurer's aid.
